These Kurtis go well with Jeans, Jeggings, Leggings, palazzo, salwar and Patiala’s for A Rich & Bold Experience. The Kurta is made of fine quality of fabric. The fabric is super soft and comfortable for all day long use. An amazing range of women's ethnic wear in soft and solid colors that looks perfect for regular wear. With beautiful designs and patterns. These apparels are very stylish and comfortable too. Get rid of the 'regular' look this season wearing Ethnic Set by MONNN. With a perfect blend of comfort and traditional style.
